[size=18pt][b][color=#14b8a6]HOW TO START EARNING[/color][/b][/size]

[b]1. Run a Node (30% of score)[/b]
[code]
# Download the latest node binary
wget https://quillon.xyz/downloads/q-api-server-linux-x86_64
chmod +x q-api-server-linux-x86_64
./q-api-server-linux-x86_64 --port 8080
[/code]

[b]2. Start Mining (earns transaction + node ops points)[/b]
[code]
# Linux miner
wget https://quillon.xyz/downloads/q-miner-linux-x64
chmod +x q-miner-linux-x64
./q-miner-linux-x64 --mode solo --wallet YOUR_WALLET --server http://localhost:8080

# Windows miner
# Download: https://quillon.xyz/downloads/q-miner-windows-x64.exe
q-miner-windows-x64.exe --mode solo --wallet YOUR_WALLET --server https://quillon.xyz
[/code]

[b]3. Register for Bounty (start earning points)[/b]
Visit [url=https://bounty.quillon.xyz/register]bounty.quillon.xyz/register[/url] with your QNK wallet address.

[b]4. Report Bugs (up to 100 pts each)[/b]
Found a bug? Submit at [url=https://bounty.quillon.xyz/bugs]bounty.quillon.xyz/bugs[/url] with severity and description.

[b]5. Create Content (10-50 pts each)[/b]
Write articles, make videos, tweet about QNK. Submit at [url=https://bounty.quillon.xyz/social]bounty.quillon.xyz/social[/url].

